    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "About Us"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "about_title",
      "label": "About Us Title",
      "default": "About Us"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "about_content",
      "label": "About Us Content",
      "default": "<p>Apricity is built through tension and refined over time.</p><p>Guided by the Three-Year Rule, we release only what proves its place. now and years from now.</p><p>Quietly considered. Meant to last.</p>"
